#: src/shared/components/Earn/Discovery/EarnFaq.tsx
msgid "GLV and Pools both enable liquidity provision on rocky, allowing users to earn fees from three revenue sources that auto-compound into the token's price. Pool tokens represent liquidity in a single pool that supports one specific market on rocky. GLV vaults contain multiple pool tokens in an auto-rebalancing composition, thereby aggregating liquidity across various markets that have the same backing tokens (ex: ETH-USDC, or BTC-USDC). Pools enable users to provide isolated liquidity with exposure to a specific market, while GLV allows users to passively earn yield from a diverse range of highly utilized pools."
msgstr "GLV 和池均可在 Rocky 上提供流動性，讓用戶從三種收入來源中賺取費用，這些費用會自動複利到代幣價格中。池代幣代表支持 Rocky 上單一特定市場的單一池中的流動性。GLV 金庫包含多個自動重新平衡的池代幣，從而聚合具有相同支持代幣（如 ETH-USDC 或 BTC-USDC）的各市場流動性。池讓用戶提供與特定市場相關的隔離流動性，而 GLV 讓用戶從多個高利用率池中被動賺取收益。"

